metadata.name: Buy The Dip
metadata.description:
Series 1 of the Stuck Yeah! Collection

Inspired by the groovy art of the 60s, this sticker is for those that just need to ‘Buy the Dip n’ chill’. Just don’t forget to take profits along the way. When times get rough, these believers just keep adding to their position, dollar-cost-averaging on the dips and holding til’ it rips.

Size: 3" x 2.05"
